{"tid":1419080,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"已經太多太多負面情緒","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:49:59.000Z","uid":211624,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ede72aff4fc224579c8ef6b0493499bdfcaba4d","tid":1419080,"uid":211624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:37:10.000Z","msg":"我知道 我都明白 依家風頭火勢嘅時候同大家講感情真係on9。<br />\n男人老狗應該係適當嘅時候做適當嘅事，各位想屌我嘅盡情屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好想同各位手足兄弟共同進退。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無奈每日出街夢遊除左係體力透支仲要接收好多負面感受，就算唔驚中彈食TG，都驚跑唔贏啲狗最後要受靶，依家見到狗都提心吊膽，即使完整咁返到屋企都要對住藍絲老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日發完夢後本身已經好攰好攰，突然收到拍拖5年嘅EX電話，佢放假由台灣返左黎香港順便支持反送中，今日仲要同我係同一個地方發夢，以為你打電話黎係擔心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滿懷期待咁接起電話<br />\n🙋🏻&zwj;♂️：「喂？做咩吖？」<br />\n<br />\n🙆🏻&zwj;♀️：「你依家散到安全未！」<br />\n<br />\n🙆🏻&zwj;♂️：「Ok啦，不過班狗發癲咁開槍啵，妳有無受傷？」<br />\n<br />\n💁🏻&zwj;♀️：「我無事吖，你依家得唔得閒吖？我打黎係想同你講樣嘢」<br />\n<br />\n🤷🏻&zwj;♂️：「咩？」<br />\n<br />\n🙍🏻&zwj;♀️：「其實呢...我已經同XXX一齊左幾日...」<br />\n<br />\n🙍🏻&zwj;♂️：「oh～<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗯...」<br />\n<br />\n個心噏一噏 <br />\n我除左同自己講無事之外咩都做唔到..<br />\n點解要係哩個時候話俾我知？<br />\n同手足返屋企一路上我都控制住自己<br />\n但係當我返屋企攤係張床<br />\n抬頭見到我地合照嘅時候<br />\n我知自己已經到左極限<br />\n內心已經支爆左<br />\n慢慢開始覺得個世界好靜<br />\n係張床呆坐左唔知幾耐<br />\n個腦點都轉唔到 越黎越亂..<br />\n消化唔到負面情緒<br />\n就算各位點樣屌我都好<br />\n我真係攰啦<br />\n對唔住各位前線手足<br />\n我真係好想消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位可以努力埋我果份<br />\n香港嘅未來係靠大家啦<br />\n最後講翻句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ccd2dcd4c6ececce90d5000b8928196fe45bff4","tid":1419080,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:46:34.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩⋯ 老土講句加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdcb2eb43f6cfb73e76dbb74af30d01647ab97e","tid":1419080,"uid":211624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ccd2dcd4c6ececce90d5000b8928196fe45bff4","tid":1419080,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:46:34.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩⋯ 老土講句加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"b48461fcfd9751a05888a1fb3b2c570381ac4210","tid":1419080,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:16:49.000Z","msg":"加啊"},{"pid":"3cfea65b4b5c52c2dbfa882a460b451d760b7132","tid":1419080,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:17:02.000Z","msg":"加油加油啊💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻🙏🏼"},{"pid":"6d23d81f8b190a99247bc81090f28ab41524e4b3","tid":1419080,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:17:42.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736358f07098b5a11f28546fce3f532e550e5e10","tid":1419080,"uid":286305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:21:59.000Z","msg":"負皮係俾條女嘅 加油呀你"},{"pid":"2e0d90b1f1087a92ec31dc0fd62c14f387907238","tid":1419080,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"巴打(拍肩)<br />\n會過去架 加油！"},{"pid":"6dc8049eb6e38b69450c94d3feb5d70f1c5a489f","tid":1419080,"uid":136377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"條女真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}